{"id:": "/div[1]", "tag": "div", "attributes": {"type": "article", "{http://www.w3.org/XML/1998/namespace}id": "MG-1678-04_003", "resp": "mercure"}, "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/head[1]", "tag": "head", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/head[1]/text()[1]", "text": "[Madrigal à Iris]"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/bibl[1]", "tag": "bibl", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/bibl[1]/title[1]", "tag": "title", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/bibl[1]/title[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Mercure galant"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/bibl[1]/text()[1]", "text": ", avril 1678 [tome 4], p. 3-5."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[1]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Voyez, Madame, par ce Madrigal si je présume trop du cours que vous m’avez fait avoir dans le monde."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]", "tag": "quote", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/label[1]", "tag": "label", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/label[1]/text()[1]", "text": "MADRIGAL."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]", "tag": "lg", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[1]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Au Mercure nouveau c’est en vain qu’on prétend,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[2]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[2]/text()[1]", "text": "Iris, sans avanture on n’y peut tenir rang."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[3]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[3]/text()[1]", "text": "Sans la Guerre ou l’Amour on n’aura point la gloire"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[4]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[4]/text()[1]", "text": "De voir son Nom dans ses Ecrits galans,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[5]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[5]/text()[1]", "text": "C’est leur unique employ de chanter la victoire"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[6]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[6]/space[1]", "tag": "space", "children": []}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[6]/space[2]", "tag": "space", "children": []}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[6]/text()[1]", "text": "Ou des Soldats ou des Amans ;"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[7]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[7]/text()[1]", "text": "La Guerre apparemment a pour vous peu de charmes,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[8]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[8]/space[1]", "tag": "space", "children": []}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[8]/space[2]", "tag": "space", "children": []}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[8]/text()[1]", "text": "Et vous fuyez ses tristes coups."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[9]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[9]/space[1]", "tag": "space", "children": []}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[9]/text()[1]", "text": "Vous aimez mieux qu’en vous rendant les armes"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[10]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[10]/text()[1]", "text": "On ne connoisse point d’autre vainqueur que vous."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[11]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[11]/text()[1]", "text": "Hé bien, suivez l’Amour, vous irez au Mercure ;"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[12]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[12]/text()[1]", "text": "Mais laissant vostre cœur, capable de ses feux,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[13]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[13]/text()[1]", "text": "Souvenez-vous, Iris, que pour une Avanture"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[14]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[14]/space[1]", "tag": "space", "children": []}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[14]/space[2]", "tag": "space", "children": []}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[14]/text()[1]", "text": "Il faut tout au moins estre deux."}]}]}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[2]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[2]/text()[1]", "text": "Quoy qu’en dise ce Madrigal, il n’est point besoin d’estre de concert pour se donner le plaisir de produire une Avanture. Il l’en naist que trop tous les jours que les Interessez ne peuvent prévoir, & qui ont quelquefois de fâcheuses apparences, quoy que dans le fond il n’y ait rien de plus innocent."}]}]}